# Custom REST API  ## items project

## Description
This project is a REST API built with Node.js and Express.
It uses a JSON file as a database instead of MongoDB.

## How it works
- Data is stored in data/items.json
- ReadFile reads data
- WriteFile updates data
- Controllers handle logic
- Routes handle endpoints

## Endpoints

GET /items → get all items  
GET /items/:id → get one item  
POST /items → create item  
PUT /items/:id → update item  
DELETE /items/:id → delete item  

## Validation
- All fields are required
- Rating must be a number

## Error Handling
- 400 → bad request
- 404 → not found
- 500 → server error
